1. create install script that is accessible from github:

	 curl raw.githubusercontent.com/..../install.sh | sudo bash
	  - check os (mac, linux)
	  - get latest release (should do CI/CD first)
	  - download latest version & copy it to /user/local/bin/vermin
	  - cp https://raw.githubusercontent.com/..../etc/keys/vermin_rsa .vermin/

	** example: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/habitat-sh/habitat/master/components/hab/install.sh
				https://get.docker.com/

2. use progress (indeterminate)

3. Logo drawing
